==English==

===Etymology===
Shortened form of the phrase "''if the shoe fits, wear it''".

===Idiom===
'''[[if]] [[the]] [[shoe]] [[fit]]s'''

# {{idiom}} If it has all of the [[characteristic]]s of a thing it likely ''is'' that thing.
#: ''"Everyone keeps calling me a bully!" "Well, '''if the shoe fits...'''"''